data.description: Remodeled home 15 min from Brickell, and South Beach. 5 min from Little Havana and the airport. The home is also just minutes from Downtown, Coconut Grove, and the Beaches. The home has an updated kitchen that includes quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, indoor laundry, and beautiful shaker-style cabinetry. Modern bathrooms with marble and tile finishes and all PVC plumbing. Updated electrical panel and 3-year-old A/C. Lush landscaping on a fenced corner lot. The parcel is zoned R2 as a duplex.    This home is centrally located. You'll enjoy all that Miami has to offer from this location.
